videos.description: Trayce Jackson-Davis spins on his Nebraska defender as he works his way to the hoop for a one-handed slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Indiana's Jackson spins for powerful slam) 2020/3/11

videos.headline: Indiana's Jackson spins for powerful slam

videos.description: Nebraska football players Brant Banks and Noah Vedral are suited up and on the bench for the Huskers' basketball team and are eligible to play if needed.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Huskers football players ready for hoops debut) 2020/3/11

videos.headline: Huskers football players ready for hoops debut

videos.description: Off Jerome Hunter's block, Indiana's Devonte Green pulls up for a 3-pointer on the other end to extend the Hoosiers' lead over Nebraska.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Indiana keeps it rolling in the 2nd half with block and 3) 2020/3/11

videos.headline: Indiana keeps it rolling in the 2nd half with block and 3

videos.description: Brant Banks and Noah Vedral check into the game in the final 3 minutes of action with Nebraska down 85-64 to Indiana in the 1st Round of the Big Ten Conference tournament.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Nebraska, Indiana fans erupt when Huskers football players check in) 2020/3/11

videos.headline: Nebraska, Indiana fans erupt when Huskers football players check in
